Iron Heart (Strike)
Level: Warblade 2
Initiation Action: 1 standard action
Range: Melee attack
Target: One creature

This maneuver allows you to combine a disarm attempt with a normal attack. You make a single melee attack as part of this strike. If this attack hits, you can also attempt to disarm your opponent. This disarm attempt does not provoke attacks of opportunity, nor is there any risk that your foe can disarm you.
